le_e632815c1391579ec\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>AI analyzes data, personalizes care, automates tasks, develops new treatments and therapies, and supports decision-making.</p>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-e9e920501f6f760d5 fusion-toggle-has-divider\" style=\"--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);--awb-content-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_e9e920501f6f760d5\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"e9e920501f6f760d5\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-14260-2\" data-target=\"#e9e920501f6f760d5\" href=\"#e9e920501f6f760d5\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-circle fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-adjust fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">How do healthcare technology solutions improve preventive care?</span></a></h4></div><div id=\"e9e920501f6f760d5\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_e9e920501f6f760d5\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>Health data collection, personalized recommendations, chronic disease management, awareness campaigns, and communication enhancement.</p>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-a3a2b30de94610e5c fusion-toggle-has-divider\" style=\"--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);--awb-content-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_a3a2b30de94610e5c\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"a3a2b30de94610e5c\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-14260-2\" data-target=\"#a3a2b30de94610e5c\" href=\"#a3a2b30de94610e5c\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-circle fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-adjust fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">What are some examples of IoT devices in healthcare, and how do they benefit patients?</span></a></h4></div><div id=\"a3a2b30de94610e5c\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_a3a2b30de94610e5c\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>Smart inhalers, implantable sensors, glucose meters, pillboxes, and wearable trackers, all benefitting patient health management and provider insights.</p>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-b78aeea8e93b171c0 fusion-toggle-has-divider\" style=\"--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);--awb-content-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_b78aeea8e93b171c0\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"b78aeea8e93b171c0\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-14260-2\" data-target=\"#b78aeea8e93b171c0\" href=\"#b78aeea8e93b171c0\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-circle fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-adjust fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">How does artificial intelligence personalize healthcare, and does it replace human doctors?</span></a></h4></div><div id=\"b78aeea8e93b171c0\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_b78aeea8e93b171c0\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>AI analyzes individual data to personalize care plans and interventions, but it does not replace human doctors – it assists and enhances their decision-making.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>\n","date":"2023-12-14T13:42:24","author":{"node":{"name":"Sanjay Kumar","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12cd5109e81ca7f47c3bdfd017c1351234efe746c16d7811a74